General.Name: Going Public Media Aktiengesellschaft
General.Description: Going Public Media Aktiengesellschaft operates as a media house for corporate finance and investment issues in Germany. The company publishes magazine, operates Web platforms, offers online newsletters, and event activities. It also offers print, online event, and network services. The company's media platform focuses on the capital market, family businesses/medium-sized businesses, and life sciences. The company was founded in 1998 and is based in Munich, Germany.
